gomodel:SYNGO_88  a       owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: PMCA2 is highly enriched in docked vesicles/active zone membrane fraction relative to free SV fraction.\nSimilar ratio found for PMCA1 in the same paper.\n\n18/01/2017 Pim Note\n- Because enriched in AZ and not in free SV AT2B2 is presumably localized to the AZ membrane, not in SVs.. Experimental description: Results: \"To isolate docking complexes from **rat brain**, we first prepared synaptosomes and subjected them to limited proteolysis to dissociate pre- and postsynaptic membranes (Figure 1A).\" p. 286" , "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0099059 replaced by GO:0048787" ;
